    Artist's Home - Villa & Private Courtyard - 200m2

    • 7 Guests
    • 3 Bedrooms
    • 3 Beds
    • 2 Bathrooms

    Looking for a spacious and peaceful space? Discover this unique residence just 20 minutes from the heart of Paris (Tram, Metro, Bus). You can easily park on the street (paid parking).

    This former artist's workshop has been completely renovated with care. The house is divided into two distinct parts, separated by a central courtyard, a rare haven of peace in Paris. Enjoy the tranquility and relax on the sun loungers after a long day of exploration.
